Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.39,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}ぐるぐる廻せ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:11.50,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}この魔法の杖で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:17.53,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}涙とSunny day 混ぜたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:21.24,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}淋しがりやさん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:23.44,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}夢は叶うよ　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:32.77,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}いつだって　一緒だよ 私たち
