Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:20.60,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}那時候的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:24.34,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}對著無法起飛的螺旋槳做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:28.80,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}朝著天空的另一半抬頭望去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:31.91,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}光著腳丫肆意奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:36.35,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們永遠都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:43.44,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}無論誤會與否 就是對生活充滿自信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:56.79,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}如同把重要的寶物 藏起來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:02:05.39,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}再也無法發現那顆深藏起來的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.39,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}咕嚕咕嚕轉上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:11.50,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}用這根魔法之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:17.53,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}把眼淚和晴天混合起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:21.24,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}怕寂寞的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:23.44,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}夢想一定會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:32.77,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我們要永遠在一起哦
